Hey!!
 Well I went to Florida we left Monday the 9th and came back Sunday 15th! It was a lot of fun we went to Disneyland and Universal Studios!! Both parks were great except we didn't get to go anywhere else cause Hurricane Charley got to us on Friday Night! It was a big experience for us!! Other then that I had a great Vacation over there. Well I'm currently not seeing anyone right now ......this past friday well I kinda went out with my friend which wasn't a great idea! Well today I'm gonna go get my schedule for school!! Not all that excited about going back but it's better then being home all day right!?! Well I don't know what else to say so gtg now!!
                                Luv Lots!!
                                    *Steph*

Hey!!
  Well last night was not the greatest night!! The guy I thought I could actully have something with turn out to be an asshole too!! He started talking to his ex again so he might get back w/her. Well good luck to him ...but it really got me mad cause I got sick for going out with him and he told me all kinds of nice stuff and now it's like he never meant any of it. Well I don't know why I'm going through so much shit but it better all be for a good reason. Well I'm just giving up on guys right now there too much drama...I rather stay single and just have fun on my own. Well it turns out that I might go to Orlando Florida for vacation!!:D I'm really excited about that...I hope we do go ..at least I can have something to look forward on. Well gtg now bye!!
                                    Luv Lots!!
                                       *Steph*

Hey!!
Well this weekend I got pretty sick and I think it's cause I went out w/this guy too much and he was sick so he got me sick!! I'm pretty dumb for doing that but oh well I like kissing him!LoL all crzy but yeah.                                              Steph**

Hey Everyone!!
Well A lot has happened This past year!! Let me start ...One of my ex-boyfriends wanted to hook up with me again during the school year ..well we begin talking and I waited 4 months for him and now all of a sudden he doesn't want anything to do with me!! I was really sad at first cause I dissed a lot of really nice guys for him and now it's like all over!! He said we can still be friends and that's cool n all but I think it's messed up that he made me wait this hole time and then change his mind!!Well I told him I moved on to another guy and guess what ??!! I did!!! I'm so happy ..the guy I moved on too is one of the guys I had to diss b4 but it turns out he still like's me and well I like him too!! We already talked about everything and well were hoping we can get together later on !! I guess everything happened for a reason!! Well I don't want to get my hopes high cause that's what I did before and it turned out bad so im just gonna let everything happen when it's suppose to happen. Well I gtg now !! Bye!!

                                Luv lots!!
                                      **Steph**
